The third likely category is cs.THEORY (Theoretical Computer Science), as the paper provides new techniques for proving negative results about computation in tile assembly. The fourth likely category is cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), as the paper deals with nanoscale self-assembling molecular systems, which are an emerging technology.
